    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "PACIFIC NORTHWEST\nNORTHWEST ORIENT AIRLINES",
      "POST CARD\nPACIFIC NORTHWEST\nPicture Lake and Mt.\nShuksan\nare\nexcellent ex-\namples of the special beauty of the\nPacific North-\nwest.\nVast forests\nsurround\nsun-drenched\nthroughout this\ngreat\nvacation\nlakes\nland. Northwest\njets serve the Pacific Northwest from\ncontinental U.S.A. as well is Hawaii, Alaska, and\nthe Orient.\n241-TRAD-454\nPRINTED IN U.S.A.\nNORTHWEST Orient AIRLINES\nPLACE\nSTAMP\nHERE\n2015.166.1148"
    ],
